{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/\uc774\uc2a4\ucf00\uc774\ud504\uc11c\ubc14\uc774\ube0c\uc775\uc2a4\ud1a0\ud2b8.gif?t=1733466320\" />Escape, Survive, and Extort</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hunter\u2019s Arena: Revolution is an exhilarating and adventurous action set in the Ancient East. Combine various skills, equipment, and tactics to survive and escape a world full of enemies. If you don\u2019t, you may lose all your precious belongings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/\ubc30\uacbd\uc0f7.gif?t=1733466320\" />In In Ancient Asia </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hunter\u2019s Arena\u2019s expansive map is filled with exquisite oriental beauty. At the same time, the solemness of the ruins of war exists. This is a place where all the resources are rare. Explore hidden locations to obtain these various resources. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, you must be careful at all times to ensure survival. Between the buildings and the forest, there are many others like yourself looking for resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/\uc2a4\ud0ac.gif?t=1733466320\" />A a Strategic Battle with Various Weapons &amp; Skills </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fortunately, your character is a natural fighter and can fight with any weapon. Survive using weapons and skills that are appropriate for each situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013930/extras/\uce90\ub9ad\ud130__1_.gif?t=1733466320\" />The Last Survivor Takes All</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survivors have everyt